		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(124767585, 'The site is well organized and easy to navigate.  There is no ambiguity about what is expected.  The grading is fair.  I had a few situations where I was not able to get things done on time and the instructor was very understanding.  The audio and video lectures were a big help, and the weekly live chats were great.  I never actually took part in the chats, but I watched the archives every week and they were an immense help in finishing some of the assignments.

One thing that I particularly appreciated was Spencer Hilton''s accessibility.  Often with online courses it can feel like the material takes the lead and the instructor is almost not a part of the process.  This was not the case with Spencer.  He responded to emails in a timely manner (usually the same day that they were sent), he was active in the discussion forums and almost always replied to questions within 24 hours.  He checked my code when I was stuck on something and got back to me with enough time to work out my problems before the due date.

I took both CS 1030 and CS 1400 from Spencer Hilton and both were great courses.  I would recommend Spencer to anyone looking to take online courses in CS, and I will take more courses from him in the future if I can.');
	
