		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(166635287, 'One reason why I think we had some of the problems that we did as a class was because early on most of the class learned not to ask questions. I remember an experience where a lot of the class didn''t understand some concepts in an assignment and the way Jeremy dealt with it was by assigning more homework, yet still with not a good understanding. From then on, I noticed less questions were being asked. 
