		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(166635286, 'The course was not very well organized. I felt like most of the assignments and tests were assigned before we were given the applicable information in class. We had to complete those assignments while most of the class was unsure about them. Then, I think most of us had learning experiences when we reviewed them after we received grades that reflected the fact that we didn''t know what we were doing. 
