		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(177977966, 'I felt there was by far way too much content for one course.  I felt the content and what was required out of this course was way to much for an introduction course.  If this had been my only class then it would have been more manageable but with a full schedule it is very hard to keep up.  For an introduction course I think there should have been more time spent teaching the class how to use AutoCAD and spend more time in class working in the software to learn and ask questions while having the instructor right there to ask questions.  I felt the E-book did not provide sufficient information to be able to complete all course materials (quizzes, module assessments, ect.)  Overall it was a fun class but was a lot more than I expected to come out of a introduction course.  ');
	
