		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(178894380, 'I LOVED this class! I felt like I learned a lot AND understood it! I have taken a few science courses here at Weber and it is by far the best taught. Pro. Skopec was great about the material and helping you out if you didn''t understand it. I think that it was a great idea to put her lectures online so if you miss class or want to go over the material again you can easily do it. I think she really has this figured out and wants her students to do well, which isn''t a vibe you get from many college professors unfortunately. I wish she would also teach Human Anatomy because they definitely need a teacher like her there! Thank you so much for a good semester! ');
	
		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(178894614, 'I really liked the online lab. A lot of it was fun to do and not overly difficult to understand. It helped me understand concepts in class which was great!');
	
