I received email responses in a very timely manner. ');
	
		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(179008126, 'The Mastering A&P portions were sometimes long and didn''t seem to have a whole lot to do with what we were learning but also understanding that it is an online course and to get the knowledge needed was great. Most of the labs were really enjoyable!');
	
