		VALUES(179491161, 'A big part of the class that I really enjoyed were the assignments. Proper template class structure was heavily used, but not at a detriment to us. Most of the assignments were challenging and rewarding, with the exception of maybe the first 1 or 2. Although they were used for review, so they shouldn''t have been very difficult. 
');
	
