		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(179563698, 'Jeremy is a great a guy and is always willing to help with any questions that I needed. I always knew when I emailed I would get a quick response.');
	
		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(179563699, 'This course was very unorganized. More than half the time I had no idea what was going on or what I needed to do. Canvas was used for this course but the due dates listed in Canvas were never correct so you never knew when something was due. Assignments were given and while giving the assignment in class the instructions changed multiple times in five minutes or less. So by the end you had no idea what you were really expected to do. The books chapters were good but the review questions were not accurate with what was stated in the chapter so this made it difficult as well. The Canvas quizzes were horrible. Some questions were right. One time I took the quiz and then when I would retake that quiz the answer changed from what it was right before. The quiz questions were confusing lots of times and were not straight forward meaning you had no idea what they were really asking. Lots of questions said choose 2 or 3 answers when only 1 or 2 were correct. There needs to be tons more organization. I talked to many others outside of the class and everyone I talked to expressed the same issues. ');
	
		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(179097058, 'Teach more in AutoCAD');
	
		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(180120864, 'Should be two classes, LEED GA prep and building materials and fundamental systems');
	
		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(178897292, 'Despite the tediousness of many of the assignments I realized they were necessary when working on websites later on in the class. ');
	
		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(179105678, 'Enjoyed this lab!!');
	
		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(179601211, 'Course material was fine. Tests were just okay. I pay to learn and part of that learning is to take appropriate tests on that material, not questions meant to trick and mislead. Some of us have a hard enough time taking tests as it is. Weber has the most ridiculous method of testing of any other university I have attended! Why is it so hard for you teachers to give paper exams instead of using chi tester? Class time is no excuse! Many of my professors at the U hand out paper tests and we take them during class. This traditional style works for most instead of staring at a screen. I would also assume Weber is lazy and does not care to grade student tests and would rather the computer do it for them. I am so happy I only came here for a semester instead of continuing at Weber.');
	
		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(179006233, 'Awesome teacher! I want to take another class from her!');
	
		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(179206304, 'Dr. Scopec is very enthusiastic in class and is well organized. Her class was one of my favorite classes!');
	
