		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(190674169, 'Provide feedback! I value your insights, but I did not get many of them. I really would have liked to get meaningful thoughts and responses to what I wrote. That is one way that I can self-assess my learning and my growth. Without that feedback, the class loses some power to impact my personal and professional growth.

It sometimes felt like you were flying by the seat of your pants or that the instruction was just based on what was going on in the classroom with only a vague outline. Maybe that is not the case, but that was my perception at times.

I enjoyed the sentiment of getting student feedback on when due dates should be and how much material should be covered, but this is a master''s-level course and people can suck it up and work hard instead of cutting corners. Many of the students in the class were new to the program--even their first semester, and so their requests and feelings about the amount of work was not as valid as it could have been.');
	
