		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(198244104, 'Michelle knows what she teaches! She clearly has a passion and a love for physiology. I only have 2 complaints. 1: shes a doctor and knows her stuff. We, as students, don''t know much about the subject. I was lost a lot of the time because I just couldn''t comprehend what she was saying at times. That leads to my second complaint... the tests suck!! I failed every test, because I felt like we were being tricked and it was written as if we were med students. The tests were beyond hard!! I actually have to retake this class, and I was there almost every day in class and I studied by butt off, and went to SI sessions like crazy. I suggest, find a way for students to pass. I now have to face telling my parents that I failed a class because I wasn''t smart enough for it... ');
	
		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(198083396, 'Skopec is amazing. It was very clear that she knows what she''s talking about and provides good ways to remember important information. She is always willing to work with students and answer questions. I think the way she grades stuff is extremely fair. Dropping the lowest exam score is extremely generous and the way she weights everything is very fair. Overall, I learned so much in this class. It was one of my very favorites, even though it''s definitely challenging. Dr. Skopec is fantastic and I was very lucky to be able to learn from her! ');
	
