		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(198442266, 'At one point I went to Professor Ball during office hours and he didn''t seem interested at all in helping me.  He claimed he was busy assisting another student (even though no one else was around) and appeared eager to get me out his door.  He wasn''t clearly listening to my inquiries and therefore didn''t understand that I just had a very minor problem with the assignment; he continued to assume I needed help with the entire assignment throughout majority of our discussion.  He never directly answered my questions nor even looked at my assignment with me.  He ended the conversation with, "Just make it work" so I was left to figure out a solution on my own that didn''t necessarily fall in line with the assignment''s instructions.  This was an unsatisfying experience for me and not one that I have had before with any other professor at WSU.  I was baffled at the lack of concern that Professor Ball showed towards me as one of his students.');
	
