3 - A more legitimate concern for each of your student''s success in your class. Most professors I''ve had at WSU go to extra lengths to try and help their students succeed, and your apparent lack of response and concern made this class more stressful and less enjoyable than I expected.
4 - I got to the point where I quit answering questions asked in class because you seemed to enjoy humiliating students (even if playfully) when we answered incorrectly.');
	
