		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(205210678, 'I would say that the biggest improvement to the course would be better a better support structure/resources for the courses assignments. The professor had a pretty restrictive availability which is totally acceptable, however since he was not available on weekends or evenings  it made it difficult to troubleshoot issues with the programming assignments. Since the bulk of the assignments were based on the XV6 operating system there is by design not a lot of online resources that you would normally have. I think that in order to compensate for the more restrictive availability the professor could make the following changes. 1 Lecture videos, A short pre-recorded lecture/assignment overview video could go a long way in clearing up issues that may arise when completing assignments. 2 slides detailing important concepts that are required for a given assignment. 3 Making participation in the discussion boards mandatory. Often the best resource for figuring out bugs or issues was the discussion board, however increased participation would of been helpful. 4. Quicker turn around on grading of assignments. This would help students to know exactly where they stand in the class. Some assignments took well over a month to be given a grade.');
	
