		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(205971177, 'This is more of a problem with the course than the professor. This class is probably the most overwhelming class in the whole computer science bachelor degree program. It needs WAY more resources. Videos, PDF''s, and links to all sorts of related material. I am pretty spoiled with having resources available because of other computer science professors such as Brad Peterson and Yong Zhang and especially Delroy Brinkerhoff his classes practically have comprehensive resources his canvas courses are structured amazing. I would really recommend whoever you have teach this course needs to be way more resource happy the operating systems canvas portal should be littered with videos done both by the professor and others. I really did not have many resources to go off of besides the assignment description and my C book which was quite helpful but not enough resources it was just so much more difficult than it needed to be. With a class this difficult I would really recommend "holding students hands through it" especially through the first month or two that is when it was super crazy getting used to sooo many new things with no adequate resources to find them. All of us can look stuff up on the internet I expect vetted resources I know to be accurate when being formally instructed.');
	
