		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(206662484, 'Brad is THE BEST instructor I have ever had at Weber or any other educational facility.
He understands the thought process that students go through and understands their questions very accurately which makes learning from his so much better. He explains things in such a way that they are really easy to understand. He also checks if things make sense and pushes people to speak up when something doesn''t make sense, which is a wonderful attribute because many times (including myself) I don''t feel comfortable interrupting the lecture. Brad is always available to help students and is great at getting people to figure out the answers themselves and learn the idea''s instead of just giving them the answer.
His code that he pre-constructs for assignments is stupendous! it helps you stay on track and lets you know when you are not doing something right. It really helped me understand the concepts and application behind the ideas that we were learning. He records and uploads his lectures that allows me to re-asses the information many times and catch the small important things that I miss. I can honestly say I would not have passed this course so easily if it wasn''t for the ability to go back and listen to the lectures again.
On top of Brad being a wonderful teacher, he also has a great personality that lets you approach him without hesitation. He keeps the class lively and entertaining while at the same time getting the message across. 
Brad Peterson is without a doubt the absolute best teacher at this university. I couldn''t recommend him enough for anyone who actually wants to learn something.');
	
