		INSERT INTO EssayResponses (questionResponseID, essayResponse)
		VALUES(207186374, 'If Brad Peterson doesn''t already have tenure with Weber State, then he should be considered for it. Mr. Peterson has been one of the most helpful teachers I have had here at Weber, and thanks to his help and the help of the Computer Science departments tutors, I was able to learn a lot about C++ and do well in a class that I went into seeing as a daunting task to learn anything in. I hope that I can take more classes from Mr. Peterson in the future.

