		VALUES(209950466, 'I love that the lectures were recorded for us to access whenever we wanted. That helped a lot. It was also nice that the test questions came from the lecture material. I really appreciated that the lowest test and quiz score got dropped from the grade book. I think Dr. Skopec did everything she could to help was succeed in this course. She didn''t try to trick us or anything like that, she just wanted to make sure that we understood the material. 
